               <li><a  data-metrics='{"action":"Click Independent Booksellers","category":"Ecommerce","label":"9781982137977"}'  class="buyLink3" href="http://www.indiebound.org/book/9781982137977?aff=NPR">Independent Booksellers</a></li>
